social_posts.post_text: I’m literally in class right now but I had to take a second to make this post. I feel like this year I let y’all down and I’ve barely released music (didn’t drop a project) which makes me feel like I didn’t really do much at all! I’ve been so focused on my personal life (school, friends, league of legends) I haven’t had much time to work on music. I love music so much and I’m so lucky and fortunate to have you all as my minivans. This year has been hard for me musically and I felt like I hit a point where I didn’t know if I wanted to make music anymore, I wasn’t inspired at all and most of the songs I dropped this year were songs I made in 2021. Even so you all still showed me love by streaming my music and interacting with me on social media. Whenever you all send me a DM saying you love my music or even just post a picture of you listening to a song of mine it truly brightens my day!! I’m working on something special for y’all that will come out early next year but I don’t want to spoil it just yet!! I know I’m ranting now but the point I’m trying to get across is YOU are the reason I’m here! YOU are who pays my bills and motivates me to keep going! YOU are the reason I’m yung van, and for that I want to thank you!! I’d also like to thank @wowdemxntia , @diondugas , @guardin & @realdiskrypt for giving me guidance and motivating me when I get distracted!! Y’all have very different work ethics but you all put so much into your work and that makes me want to do better!! Let’s finish this year off strong and I can’t wait to take over 2023!!! 😊

Y’all need to up your security cause I’ve been sneaking in to do my laundry 😈 

New song just dropped w the homies @laelandd , @joshuapickus & @wowdemxntia we did a cover of “Mistletoe” by Justin Bieber!! This is the last song I’m releasing of the year but I meant it when I said 2023 is gonna be a good year I’m working on a lot of stuff behind the scenes and you all are gonna be pretty darn happy about it!! I’m so excited for next year, but until then, have a happy holiday and I’ll see y’all soon 💙

HAPPY BIRTHDAY to one of the kindest and most talented individuals I’ve ever had the pleasure of knowing!! I hope today is a good day for you and you remember that you have helped so many people with your music and if you hadn’t started making music we would have never met!! I wish you a wonderful rest of the year, I love you homie 💙

The year is coming to an end and I wanted to make a post to wrap up the year and tell you all what I’ve got planned for 2023. I feel like I didn’t do as much as I could have this year with music and part of that is because I’ve been working on something special since January and I think I’m finally ready to announce I’m releasing a new album early 2023!! I’m not ready to announce the name yet but just know the first single is dropping on January 27th and it has not 1 but 2 special features on it!! Before that comes out I did a little verse for @fxrroh and that song is going to drop on January 6th, so we are starting the year off with music right from the start!! I’m working on so much for music right now and I just want you all to know I LOVE making music and I will continue to do so until I’m dead!! With that being said I will be releasing a lot of music in 2023 and doing my absolute most to bring you great music and finally some new merch as well!! I just want to say thank you for being so supportive and I promise you it’ll all make sense soon!! I had a great time last weekend getting to see guardin perform and a bunch of really cool bands, I even got to bring my friends Marko and Matias who I’ve met from school!! That show made me realize how much more I could be doing and how I’m not close to where I can be if I put my all into this!! I know this is a long post but if you’ve made it this far I love you so much and I’m doing to do my best to make 2023 a memorable year for yung van and the minivans 💙

I’d also like to thank @fruiteas , @digiyams , and @walkerdunnvisuals for helping with the visual design of the project and singles!! Next I’d like to thank @baylesdsgn , @that_boy_lucas & @hhazelboyy for helping create the music videos for the project as well, y’all helped make this project special!! Hey minivans, the last few months have been really up and down for me in terms of my music. The album with diskrypt put a lot of stress on my music career and stopped me from being able to release music on my own. I’ve got a lot of music recorded but I can’t really release it right now which has really stressed me out since this is my job. Thankfully I’ve got something worked out with @toolost and I’m gonna be dropping a few tracks to end out the year, starting with the first single on October 6th!! Over the weekend getting to perform with guardin, Swaine & polearm was really refreshing because I hadn’t done a show in a long time!! I’m gonna be dropping some really cool songs and doing my best to give y’all a reason to keep rocking with me!! Shoutout @reservedforhell for the sick new profile picture, you are an awesome dude, I’m really glad to know you!! I’m gonna post more frequently, at least once a week on here, so I’ll see y’all soon!! I love you all bunches, thanks for being the best minivans I could ask for 💙

I want to start this post off by saying thank you to all the minivans that streamed my music this year!! It still blows my mind how supportive you all have been, I literally dropped an alt/rock album produced by @wowdemxntia and then dropped an edm album produced by @realdiskrypt but you still stayed rocking with me!! To give you all some insight to my life I graduate college in 2 weeks with a bachelors in business administration. I’ve been in college since 2017 and music has helped pay for my living expenses while I go to school. When I get my degree, I’ll have to thank you all because it wouldn’t have been possible without your support!! My last project of 2023 comes out this Friday, it’s an ep called “OPAQUE” and it’s all produced by @hkfiftyone so be sure to check it out if you like the songs we’ve made before!! Once again, I am truly so lucky to have the best fans in the world and I hope to bring you all even more music in 2024 and beyond!! I hope to make you all proud, thank you so much, I love y’all and I will be back with even more music soon 💙✨

I can’t believe that 2024 is already here. I reached top 700 in league of legends, I dropped 2 albums, I graduated from college and I started dating the most beautiful woman in the world!! I’ve been in college since 2017 and I dropped out twice, so I can’t believe I finally graduated!! I’ll make a bigger post about it once I get my diploma, but just know I am gonna do big things!! I already have an album almost finished that I’m gonna start rolling out very soon!! The first song this year is a single w/ @heysinxi and then I will start rolling out my project!! I’m going to drop a music video for each of the songs on the project, so I’ll hopefully have a lot more to post soon!! I just want to say thank you to everyone who is still around in 2024, I’ve got a lot of cool things planned and I’m stoked for y’all to see!!
